# Deploy Glitchtip on Scalingo

Create an app on Scalingo. Add env vars :

 * BUILDPACK_URL = https://github.com/Scalingo/multi-buildpack
 * GLITCHTIP_VERSION = v3.4.6

Add a Redis and a PostgreSQL addons.

Push the repo on your app. When the deployment is over, you can create an account with this procedure (run in a bash container) : https://glitchtip.com/documentation/install#django-admin .
Use the documentation ( https://glitchtip.com/documentation/install#configuration ) to fill env vars specific to Glitchtip.
